# Query Expression Language overview

A beta query language to select and aggregate data in W&B

Use the query expressions to select and aggregate data across runs and projects. Learn more about [query panels](/models/app/features/panels/query-panels).

See the public [Query panel examples report](https://wandb.ai/luis_team_test/weave_example_queries/reports/Query-Panel-Examples---Vmlldzo1NzIxOTY2) for interactive examples. For details about creating panels, stepping through run history, and configuration options such as **Concat** and **Paginate** , see the [Query panels overview](/models/app/features/panels/query-panels).

